## Compliance Check

When auditing UX and interaction design during Phase 6b, verify:

| Check | Rule | Applies To |
|-------|------|-----------|
| Commands use noun-verb grammar | IXD-001 | CLI |
| All exit codes documented | IXD-003 | CLI |
| Help text present for every command | IXD-004 | CLI |
| All states designed (loading, empty, error, success) | IXD-008 | Web |
| All forms have accessible labels | IXD-009 | Web |
| API errors use standard format | IXD-012 | API |
| List endpoints support pagination | IXD-013 | API |
| Terminology consistent across interfaces | IXD-014 | All |
| Significant flows documented | IXD-015 | All |
